Name: Stress Random
About the game: Stress Random - 2D looter shooter with random generation of levels, monsters and loot. You play as a hikka living under the surface of Mars. You are a hikka in this world, with a strange name, who does not have any duties like 'save the world, the universe, build communism, etc.' Main features: Labyrinths, battle places are generated randomly. Monsters collect body parts in the same way. Endless pumping of equipment, increasing the progress and level of cards. Deep customization system for weapons and armor. Wealth on this planet is determined by the amount of despair (this is something like an ore that you can pour into your blood). There is a casino here where you can sustainably maintain your poverty Basically, the game relies on gameplay, so there is very little thoughtful plot or philosophical context here.
